    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279310/extras/f2d97be7a6c681e356fce87bbbb6ff79.avif?t=1749380946\" width=616 height=72 /></span>欢迎回到熟悉的茜镇！现在距离彩封印之前在茜镇为非作歹的魔物已经过了两年，而人们也过上了像魔物事件发生之前一样的平静生活。然而阴谋的暗云却重新出现在了茜镇的上空，和两年前一样的诡异事件在茜镇的各处发生着。彩再次挺身而出，想要解决茜镇的困境，而这次她可并不是在孤军奋战，因为一个被谜团包裹着的女生成为了彩的盟友。这次她们能否根除潜伏在茜镇的邪恶存在，将本该属于茜镇的安宁完璧归赵呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279310/extras/bcf753632d7a0d9a44b677b997412644.avif?t=1749380946\" width=616 height=72 /></span>在熟悉的茜镇当中探索，收集能够帮助您达成您的任务目标的各种道具与信息吧！茜镇在这两年里有了不少变化，这也就意味着相比上一作而言，您能够去更多的地方探索啦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦您收集到了合适的道具与足够的信息，剧情就会自然而然地推进！随着剧情的推进，您能够解锁越来越多的新地区，一步一步地定位潜藏在茜镇中的邪恶存在并且与之正面对抗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279310/extras/3d9d8b98d41957094560571ff0b22316.avif?t=1749380946\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279310/extras/aa53007b4e603b92fbabd97d5d0cb9c1.avif?t=1749380946\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279310/extras/9e4ba03b51a3dc5dac3692217c45a95b.avif?t=1749380946\" width=616 height=399 /></span>_English</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279310/extras/918bb8b45dce0c8735e26a6f1ca6c5bf.avif?t=1749380946\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>令人流连忘返的精致像素风</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索茜镇的过程当中，也不要忘记欣赏沿途精美的像素风景哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>将冒险与解谜合二为一的游戏流程</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在茜镇的各个角落探索，并且与每一名居民深入交流吧！只有收集到了正确的道具和足够的信息，才能揭开各种各样的谜团，发现阴谋背后的真相！</p>",
